---
// FooterHero.astro
---

<section
  class="w-full min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center py-16 px-4 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-blue-100"
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-5xl font-medium leading-tight mb-6">
      Sleep tight
      <span class="text-primary">with your calendars in sync</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-800 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10">
      SynCal is a tool that allows you to automatically sync your calendars.
    </p>

    <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
      <a href="#" class="cta-primary">Start syncing your calendars today</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
